short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Never lose your place again! Backtrackinator remembers your last visited page on websites and takes you back with a single click

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
As a user, you can simply click the extension icon in the Chrome toolbar, and the extension will take you to the last visited page of the current website so you can continue to use any specific website from where you last left off. This extension does not have a settings page, and no data is stored locally.
